<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('partials/html-head', {title: ""}); -%>

<body>
  <div id="app" class="wrap">
    <header>
      <%- include('partials/nav'); -%>
      <div class="spacer"></div>
      <h1 class="page-title"><em>Veenew</em> - <span style="font-weight: normal;">Your corner of the web</span></h1>
    </header>

    <section>
      <p>Veenew (formerly Veeblog) is a simple microblogging platform at its core, but flexible enough for regular blogs, essays, journals, personal website, and everything in between.</p>
      <p>It brings the freedom of traditional blogging to microblogging - a clean space to write, share, and connect on your terms. No follows, no likes, just your thoughts.</p>

      <a href="/signup"><button>get started for free</button></a>
    </section>
    <section>
      <div class="spacer"></div>
      <div class="spacer"></div>
    </section>
    <section id="features">
      <h2>Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <h3>No Coding Skills Needed - Markdown Everything</h3>
          No technical experience required, just write in Markdown. Build your full blog or personal site effortlessly, with support for images, videos, and structured content. Create pages with clean URLs and organize everything using headings, lists, and code blocks exactly the way you want.
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>Pure Writing, Zero Distractions</h3>
          No likes, no comments, no follower counts. Just you and your words. Focus on what matters without the anxiety of social metrics or endless notifications.
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>Instant Setup</h3>
          Get your <code>username.veenew.com</code> subdomain and start posting in seconds. No complex configuration, no technical knowledge required. Sign up, choose your username, and you're live.
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>Bring Your Own Domain - Free</h3>
          Already own a domain? Point a CNAME record at us and your blog is served from <code>yourdomain.com</code> instead of the subdomain. HTTPS is set up automatically, and it costs nothing - no paid plan, no add-on.
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>Make It Yours</h3>
          Customize with your own CSS to match your style. Full control over your blog's look and feel, from minimal typography to bold custom designs.
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>Always Ad-Free</h3>
          No ads. Not now, not ever. Your space stays yours. We don't sell your attention, track your readers, or clutter your writing with promotional content.
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>RSS Built-In</h3>
          Every profile gets an RSS feed automatically - let readers follow their way. Whether they use Feedly, NewsBlur, or any RSS reader, your content is accessible beyond the web browser.
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>True Data Ownership</h3>
          Export all your content anytime. No lock-in, no questions asked. Your words belong to you, and you can take them anywhere, whenever you want.
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>No Artificial Limits</h3>
          Microblog thoughts, publish long-form essays, or mix both. Write what you want, when you want. There's no character count, no post frequency restrictions, no algorithm deciding what deserves attention.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="spacer"></div>
      <a href="/signup"><button>get started</button></a>

    </section>
    <div class="spacer"></div>
    <section id="pricing">
      <h2>Free for everyone</h2>
      <p>
        Write, publish, and share without ever paying a cent.
        All features included - custom domains, unlimited posts and pages, custom CSS - no trials, no limits, no catches.
      </p>
    </section>
    <div class="spacer"></div>
    <section>

      <blockquote><em>Just a calm corner of the internet where you can write and share on your own terms.</em></blockquote>
      <div class="spacer"></div>
      <p>Curious how it looks? View a sample profile: <a href="https://vasanth.veenew.com">vasanth.veenew.com</a></p>
    </section>

    <div class="spacer"></div>
    <%- include('partials/footer'); -%>
  </div>
</body>

</html>